data.description: Just minutes from the new Glendale Blue Oval factories, this Brick/Vinyl 3 Bed, 2 Bath 1,865 sqft home rests on a nice lot with a 24'x30' 2 car garage, outbuilding and large backyard. Property features include a fenced area for dogs, large back deck, paved driveway and room for chickens. Interior features laminate flooring, spacious living area, roomy kitchen, pantry, dining room with laundry closet and pantry.
